item.title: Michigan, Ohio State players brawl after Wolverines beat No. 2 Buckeyes. Police use pepper spray
item.description: A fight broke out at midfield after Michigan stunned No. 2 Ohio State 13-10 on Saturday when Wolverines players attempted to plant their flag on the OSU logo and were confronted by the Buckeyes.

item.title: Houston firefighters rescue dog stranded on bridge pier in chilly water
item.description: A dog is reunited with its owner after being rescued from the chilly waters of a Houston bayou. The little dog was spotted Friday stranded on a bridge pier in the Sims Bayou in southwest Houston.

item.title: Michigan upsets No. 2 Ohio State 13-10 for Wolverines’ 4th straight win over bitter rival
item.description: Dominic Zvada kicked a 21-yard field goal with 45 seconds left and Michigan stunned No. 2 Ohio State 13-10, ending the Buckeyes’ hopes of returning to the Big Ten title game.
